CustomField.description: Partners are senior lawyers at the firm. Many of the firm's lawyers, such as associates or "Of Counsel" lawyers, are not partners. We update this field based on our contacts at the firm, firm websites, or published lists like NLJ, AmLaw or Lexpert.
